---
import PageHero from '../PageHero.astro';
---

<section class="relative w-full">
  <PageHero title="About Me" eyebrow="Voyaflair" />

  <!-- Intro copy -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24 text-center">
    <p class="prose-body text-neutral-700">
      Hi, I’m Joanna — the creator behind Voyaflair.
    </p>
    <p class="prose-body text-neutral-700 mt-6">
      A curated travel space shaped by the belief that the most meaningful journeys are
      not about seeing more, but about experiencing places more deeply.
    </p>
    <p class="prose-body text-neutral-700 mt-6">
      Based in Oslo and originally from Greece, my perspective on travel has been shaped
      by the contrast between Mediterranean warmth and Scandinavian simplicity — two
      aesthetics and ways of living that continue to influence the way I experience
      places around the world.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
